{"id":"936","label":"hoverResult","result":{"contents":[{"language":"dart","value":"dart:core"},{"language":"dart","value":"DateTime toUtc()"},{"language":"dart","value":"/// Returns this DateTime value in the UTC time zone.\n///\n/// Returns [this] if it is already in UTC.\n/// Otherwise this method is equivalent to:\n///\n/// ```dart template:expression\n/// DateTime.fromMicrosecondsSinceEpoch(microsecondsSinceEpoch,\n///                                     isUtc: true)\n/// ```"}]},"type":"vertex"}
